                    <para>
                        With the <guilabel>Images Sort Order</guilabel> setting, you can select whether newly-loaded images are sorted by their date, name, or size on disk.
                    </para>

                    <para>
                        With the <guilabel>Reverse ordering</guilabel> setting, newly-loaded images will be sorted in descending order.
